description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 22, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 66, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Nine Lives for East, Nine Lives for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80223-19974-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [66 Votes, Common]
